<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body style="width:1000px;margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="text-align:center;line-height:150%">
        <strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">“SIFIC2019感控实践优秀基层医院”活动方案</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:Calibri;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一、背景</span></span></strong>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">由上海斯菲克微生物应用技术研究中心和上海市院内感染质控中心联合主办，国家卫健委能力建设和继续教育中心支持、复旦大学附属中山医院承办的第</span>15<span style="font-family:宋体">届上海国际医院感染控制论坛（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">）暨第</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">届东方耐药与感染大会（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">OCAMRI</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）联合会议（以下简称“</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC2019</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">全国年会”）定于</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2019</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">29</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">日～</span>
        <span style="font-family:Calibri">6</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">日在上海跨国采购会展中心召开。为进一步推动科学有效的医院感染防控措施在各级医疗机构的全面实施，推动各级医疗机构特别是基层医疗机构感控的基础和临床研究，促进感控的学科发展和团队建设，在国家卫健委医院管理研究所医院感染质量管理与控制中心的大力支持下，上海斯菲克微生物应用技术研究中心决定组织举办</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">“<span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC2019</span><span style="font-family:宋体">感控实践优秀基层医院”</span></span></strong>
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">活动。我们将秉承公平、公开、公正的原则，采取单位自荐的方式，让拥有感控新理念、新实践的基层医院入选。</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:Calibri;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二、评选对象与申请条件</span></span></strong>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">全国各省市（不含港澳台）基层医疗机构（地市级医院、县区级及以下医院），以医院为报名单位，共评选出</span>50 <span style="font-family:宋体">个“感控实践优秀基层医院”。</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">(<span style="font-family:宋体">一</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">) </span><span style="font-family:宋体">基本条件：</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">1.<span style="font-family:宋体">医疗机构应设立独立的医院感染管理部门；</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">2.<span style="font-family:宋体">医院感染管理部门成立时间</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年及以上；</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">3.<span style="font-family:宋体">医院感染管理部门团队成员</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">人及以上；</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">4.<span style="font-family:宋体">本单位至少有</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">人注册为上海国际医院感染控制论坛（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">）会员（中级会员及以上）</span>
        </span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">(<span style="font-family:宋体">二</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">) </span><span style="font-family:宋体">优先条件：</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2015</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年至今，符合下列任一或多项条件</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">1.<span style="font-family:宋体">本单位曾组织参加由国家医院感染质量管理与控制中心举办的</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">“感·动中国”基层医院感染质量管理培训班</span></strong>
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">2.<span style="font-family:宋体">本单位员工以第一作者或通讯作者正式发表在国家统计源及以上期刊杂志的感控相关论文至少</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">篇；</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">3.<span style="font-family:宋体">本单位员工有担任医院感染控制相关学会（含质控中心）的全国委员，或省市（直辖市）常务委员及以上学术兼职；</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">4.<span style="font-family:宋体">本单位员工有在医院感染相关的省级及以上继续医学教育培训班上讲课，或在市级及以上医院感染相关年会上做专题学术报告；</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">5.<span style="font-family:宋体">本单位员工有参与过医院感染相关书籍的编写；</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">6.<span style="font-family:宋体">本单位员工有被评为</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC</span><span style="font-family:宋体">优秀版主、优秀会员、最佳辩手、创作达人等荣誉；或近</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">年在</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC</span><span style="font-family:宋体">感染网、</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC</span><span style="font-family:宋体">感染官微上发表原创文章</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">5</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">篇以上或任职编辑、审稿等岗位。</span>
        </span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">7.<span style="font-family:宋体">本单位曾使用</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC</span><span style="font-family:宋体">考试云对全院员工进行医院感染相关知识与技能的考核。</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:rgb(255,0,0);font-size:16px">8.<span style="font-family:宋体">本单位在医院感染防控方面有突出亮点（医院支持力度、工作成效、地区引领等）</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、申报材料</span></span></strong>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">．详细填写附表“</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">SIFIC2019<span style="font-family:宋体">感控实践优秀基层医院</span></span></strong>
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">”申报表</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">2<span style="font-family:宋体">．您认为最有代表性的已发表的</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">2</span><span style="font-family:宋体">篇论文（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">PDF</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">格式，如有）</span>
        </span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">3<span style="font-family:宋体">．省市级及以上学会（含质控中心）任职聘书扫描件（如有）</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">4. &nbsp;<span style="font-family:宋体">其它证明材料（如有）</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></strong>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">四</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">、奖励措施</span></span></strong>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">1.<span style="font-family:宋体">资助入选医院一名团队成员全额免费参与</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC2019</span><span style="font-family:宋体">全国年会。资助内容包括：免会务费、资料费、会议期间的住宿费和往返上海的长途交通费（</span>
        <span style="font-family:Calibri">T/K/Z</span><span style="font-family:宋体">之硬卧，高铁二等座，不含机票）；</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">2.<span style="font-family:宋体">颁发</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC</span><span style="font-family:宋体">“</span></span><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">感</span>·动中国丨<span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC2019</span><span style="font-family:宋体">基层感控百佳医院”</span></span></strong>
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">荣誉证书。</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:Calibri;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;line-height: 150%;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">五、截止时间</span></span></strong>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">申报截止时间为</span>2019<span style="font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">4</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">19</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">日，电子版申报表、发表论文（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">PDF </span><span style="font-family:宋体">格式）、其他相关证明材料（图片或</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">PDF</span><span style="font-family:宋体">格式），压缩成zip或rar格式文件上传</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">。</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">1</span><span style="font-family:宋体">日</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">-15</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">日组委会进行终评；</span>
        <span style="font-family:Calibri">5</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">16</span><span style="font-family:宋体">日后公布入选名单。</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">有关评选的信息，将在上海国际医院感染控制论坛（</span>SIFIC<span style="font-family:宋体">）的相关版块（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">bbs.sific.com.cn</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）、</span>
        <span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC</span><span style="font-family:宋体">感染网（</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">www.sific.com.cn</span><span style="font-family:宋体">）、</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC</span><span style="font-family:宋体">感染官微（</span>
        <span style="font-family:Calibri">SIFIC2007</span>
        <span style="font-family:宋体">）公布。</span>
        </span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height: 150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span>
    </p>
    <p style="line-height: 150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span>
    </p>
    <p style="text-align:right;line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">上海斯菲克微生物应用技术研究中心</span></span>
    </p>
    <p style="text-align:right;line-height:150%">
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px">2019<span style="font-family:宋体">年</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">月</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">27</span><span style="font-family:宋体">日</span></span>
        <span style=";font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:16px"><br/></span>
    </p>
    <p>
        <br/>
    </p>
